title: Slow Cooker Bourbon Street Chicken
directions: Place frozen chicken thighs on bottom of crock pot. Combine remaining ingredients and pour over chicken. Cook 8 hours on low, then shred chicken in the slow cooker to a "pulled pork" consistency. Ladle over a bowl of brown rice or place atop a whole-grain bun. (Not included in Nutrition Facts).
ingredients: 1 clove garlic, chopped (or 1 tbsp. granulated garlic)
